Package net.cloud.client.nio.packet.packets

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ButtonActionPacket
    A packet to tell the server about some button being acted on.
    CompositePacket
    A CompositePacket is a Packet made up of other Packets.
    LoginPacket
    Deals with the login process.
    LoginPacket.LoginDataRequestPacket
    A request we will send to the server once our login information has been verified.
    LoginPacket.LoginDataResponsePacket
    We've gotten the login data we need! This is the last packet in the login process.
    LoginPacket.LoginResponsePacket
    This packet is received by the client after we request to login.
    LogoutPacket
    The server is telling us to log out when we receive this packet
    PacketManager
    In short, keeps a record of the different packets.
    ShowMessageDialogPacket
    A packet that asks us to show a message dialog
    TestPacket
    Packet for testing stuff.
